	units directly to the public at the public offering price listed
	on the cover page of this prospectus and part to certain dealers
	at a price that represents a concession not in excess of $0.594
	a unit under the public offering price. After the initial
	offering of the common units, the offering price and other
	selling terms may from time to time be varied by the
	representatives. The offering of the common units by the
	underwriters is subject to receipt and acceptance and subject to
	the underwriters right to reject any order in whole or in
	part.


	 


